Symbol.Script_2D:
pen gs_cont_pen fill gs_fill_type
! ----------------------------------------------------------------------------- ! 2D Hotspots ! -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
unID=1
hotspot2 A/2, 0, unID : unID = unID + 1
if iDispenserstyle = 1 then hotspot2 A/2, -B/2, unID : unID = unID + 1
hotspot2 0, 0, unID, A, 1+256 : unID=unID+1 hotspot2 A, 0, unID, A, 2 : unID=unID+1 hotspot2 -A, 0, unID, A, 3 : unID=unID+1
hotspot2 0, -B, unID, A, 1+256 : unID=unID+1 hotspot2 A, -B, unID, A, 2 : unID=unID+1 hotspot2 -A, -B, unID, A, 3 : unID=unID+1
hotspot2 0, 0, unID, B, 1+256 : unID=unID+1 hotspot2 0, -B, unID, B, 2 : unID=unID+1 hotspot2 0, B, unID, B, 3 : unID=unID+1
hotspot2 A, 0, unID, B, 1+256 : unID=unID+1 hotspot2 A, -B, unID, B, 2 : unID=unID+1 hotspot2 A, B, unID, B, 3 : unID=unID+1 endif
if iDispenserstyle = 2 then if iSymbolType = SYMBTYPE_DETAILED then hotspot2 0 - FrameWidth, 0, unID : unID=unID+1 hotspot2 A + FrameWidth, 0, unID : unID=unID+1 endif
hotspot2 0 + BoxThk + 0.01, -RollRadius - RollRadius*0.25 - 0.01 - 0.004, unID : unID=unID+1 hotspot2 A - BoxThk - 0.01 , -RollRadius - RollRadius*0.25 - 0.01 - 0.004, unID : unID=unID+1
hotspot2 0, 0, unID, A, 1+256 : unID=unID+1 hotspot2 -1, 0, unID, A, 3+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot2 A, 0, unID, A, 2 : unID=unID+1
hotspot2 0, 0, unID, B, 1+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot2 0, -1, unID, B, 3+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot2 0, B, unID, B, 2 : unID=unID+1
hotspot2 A, 0, unID, B, 1+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot2 A, -1, unID, B, 3+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot2 A, B, unID, B, 2 : unID=unID+1 endif
if iDispenserstyle = 3 then if iSymbolType = SYMBTYPE_DETAILED then hotspot2 0 - FrameWidth, 0, unID : unID=unID+1 hotspot2 A + FrameWidth, 0, unID : unID=unID+1 endif
hotspot2 0 + BoxThk + 0.01, -RollRadius + 0.01, unID : unID=unID+1 hotspot2 A - BoxThk - 0.01, -RollRadius + 0.01, unID : unID=unID+1
hotspot2 A/2 , 0, unID : unID=unID+1
hotspot2 0, 0, unID, A, 1+256 : unID=unID+1 hotspot2 -1, 0, unID, A, 3+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot2 A, 0, unID, A, 2 : unID=unID+1
hotspot2 0, 0, unID, B, 1+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot2 0, -1, unID, B, 3+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot2 0, B, unID, B, 2 : unID=unID+1
hotspot2 A, 0, unID, B, 1+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot2 A, -1, unID, B, 3+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot2 A, B, unID, B, 2 : unID=unID+1 endif
if iDispenserstyle = 4 then hotspot2 0, 0, unID : unID = unID + 1 hotspot2 A, 0, unID : unID = unID + 1 hotspot2 A, -B, unID : unID = unID + 1 hotspot2 0, -B, unID : unID = unID + 1 endif
! ----------------------------------------------------------------------------- ! Styles ! ----------------------------------------------------------------------------- add2 A/2, 0 gosub iDispenserstyle del 1 end
! ============================================================================= ! SUBRUTINES ! ! =============================================================================
! ----------------------------------------------------------------------------- ! Wall Mounted Toilet Paper dispenser ! -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
1: add2 -a/2, 0 line2 0, -0.002, a, -0.002 line2 0, -0.01, a, -0.01
poly2_b 13, 7, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, 0, -b, 1, a, -b, 1, a, -0.01, 1, a-0.005, -0.01, 1, a-0.005, -0.002, 1, a, -0.002, 1, a, 0, 1, 0, 0, 1, 0, -0.002, 1, 0.005, -0.002, 1, 0.005, -0.01, 1, 0, -0.01, 1, 0, -b, -1 del 1 return
! ----------------------------------------------------------------------------- ! Built-in 1 Toilet Paper dispenser ! -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
2: add2 0, b line_type CabinetLineType add2 0,0 poly2_b 5,3, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, -A*0.5, 0, 3, A*0.5, 0, 3, A*0.5, -B, 0, -A*0.5, -B, 3, -A*0.5, 0, 3
if iSymbolType = SYMBTYPE_SIMPLE then line2 -A*0.5, -B, A*0.5, -B del 1
add2 A*0.5, -B
if iSymbolType = SYMBTYPE_DETAILED then line_type 1 poly2_b 5,3, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, -A-FrameWidth, 0, 3, FrameWidth, 0, 3, FrameWidth, -FrameThk, 3, -A-FrameWidth, -FrameThk, 3, -A-FrameWidth, 0, 3 endif del 2
! --- Toilet Tissue --- if iSymbolType = SYMBTYPE_DETAILED then add2 -a/2 + BoxThk + 0.01, -FrameThk poly2_b 5,3, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, A-(BoxThk)*2-0.02, 0, 1, 0, 0, 1, 0, -RollRadius-RollRadius*0.25-0.01+FrameThk-0.004, 1, A-(BoxThk)*2-0.02, -RollRadius-RollRadius*0.25-0.01+FrameThk-0.004, 1, A-(BoxThk)*2-0.02, 0, 3 del 1 else line_type 1 add2 -a/2 + BoxThk + 0.01, 0 poly2_b 5,3, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, A-(BoxThk)*2-0.02, 0, 1, 0, 0, 1, 0, -RollRadius-RollRadius*0.25-0.01-0.004, 1, A-(BoxThk)*2-0.02, -RollRadius-RollRadius*0.25-0.01-0.004, 1, A-(BoxThk)*2-0.02, 0, 3 del 1 endif
return
! ----------------------------------------------------------------------------- ! Built-in 2 Toilet Paper dispenser ! -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
3:
! --- Cabinet --- add2 0, B line_type CabinetLineType add2 0,0 poly2_b 5,3, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, -A*0.5, 0, 3, A*0.5, 0, 3, A*0.5, -B, 0, -A*0.5, -B, 3, -A*0.5, 0, 3
if iSymbolType = SYMBTYPE_SIMPLE then line2 -A*0.5, -B, A*0.5, -B del 1
add2 A*0.5, -B if iSymbolType = SYMBTYPE_DETAILED then line_type 1 poly2_b 5,3, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, -A-FrameWidth, 0, 3, FrameWidth, 0, 3, FrameWidth, -FrameThk, 3, -A-FrameWidth, -FrameThk, 3, -A-FrameWidth, 0, 3 endif del 2
! --- Toilet Tissue --- if iSymbolType = SYMBTYPE_DETAILED then add2 -a/2 + BoxThk + 0.01, -FrameThk poly2_b 5,3, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, A-(BoxThk)*2-0.02, 0, 1, 0, 0, 1, 0, -RollRadius+FrameThk+0.01, 1, A-(BoxThk)*2-0.02, -RollRadius+FrameThk+0.01, 1, A-(BoxThk)*2-0.02, 0, 3 del 1 else line_type 1 add2 -a/2 + BoxThk + 0.01, 0 poly2_b 5,3, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, A-(BoxThk)*2-0.02, 0, 1, 0, 0, 1, 0, -RollRadius+0.01, 1, A-(BoxThk)*2-0.02, -RollRadius+0.01, 1, A-(BoxThk)*2-0.02, 0, 3 del 1 endif
return
! ----------------------------------------------------------------------------- ! Commercial Toilet Paper dispenser ! -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
4: circle2 0, -b/2, lockDia/2 poly2_b 4, 1+2+4, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, -a/2, 0, 1, a/2, 0, 1, a/2, -b, 1, -a/2, -b, 1 return
Symbol.Script_1D:
! const values for parameter: iDetlevel3D DETLEVEL3D_DETAILED = 1 DETLEVEL3D_SIMPLE = 2 DETLEVEL3D_OFF = 3 dim typRes[3] typRes[1] = `Detailed` typRes[2] = `Simple` typRes[3] = `Off`
eps = 0.0001
! const values for parameter: iDispenserstyle DISPENSERSTYLE_WALLMOUNTED = 1 DISPENSERSTYLE_BUILTIN1 = 2 DISPENSERSTYLE_BUILTIN2 = 3 DISPENSERSTYLE_COMMERCIAL = 4 dim stStyles[4] stStyles[1] = `Wall Mounted` stStyles[2] = `Built-in 1` stStyles[3] = `Built-in 2` stStyles[4] = `Commercial`
! const values for parameter: iSymbolType SYMBTYPE_DETAILED = 1 SYMBTYPE_SIMPLE = 2 dim stSymbTypes[2] stSymbTypes[1] = `Detailed` stSymbTypes[2] = `Simple`
! ----------------------------------------------------------------------------- ! Geometry parameters for Built-in 1 and Built-in 2 ! -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
FrameWidth = 0.02 FrameThk = 0.005 BoxThk = 0.004
! ----------------------------------------------------------------------------- ! Geometry parameters for Commercial ! -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
cabDepth = 0.11 !Cabinet Depth doorFrameDepth = b - cabDepth !Door Frame Depth frontInsetDepth = 0.003 !Front Inset Thickness bottomDepth = b - 0.01 !Bottom Cabinet Depth paperDia = 0.22 !Paper Diameter paperDepth = 0.11 !Paper Depth lockDia = 0.02 !Lock Diameter lockHeight = 0.005 !Lock Height
Symbol.Script_UI:
ui_dialog `Toilet Paper Dispenser Style`
ui_infield{3} "iDispenserstyle", 0, 5, 444, 260, 1, 1, 4, 1, 132, 128, 85, 85, 1, stStyles[1], 1, 2, stStyles[2], 2, 3, stStyles[3], 3, 4, stStyles[4], 4
Symbol.Script_VL:
! --- Bottom, Top Level Calculation --- ac_toplevel = topHeight ac_bottomlevel = ac_toplevel - ZZYZX parameters ac_toplevel = ac_toplevel, ac_bottomlevel = ac_bottomlevel
call "FM_types_BA_WMCC" parameters all
! ----------------------------------------------------------------------------- ! 3D detlevel ! -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
values{2} "iDetlevel3D" DETLEVEL3D_DETAILED, typRes[1], DETLEVEL3D_SIMPLE, typRes[2], DETLEVEL3D_OFF, typRes[3]
values "gs_resol" range [4,)
if iDetlevel3D = DETLEVEL3D_SIMPLE then hideparameter "gs_resol" lock "gs_resol" endif if iDetlevel3D = DETLEVEL3D_OFF then hideparameter "gs_resol", "gs_shadow" lock "gs_resol", "gs_shadow" endif
! ----------------------------------------------------------------------------- ! Styles ! ----------------------------------------------------------------------------- values{2} "iDispenserstyle" DISPENSERSTYLE_WALLMOUNTED, stStyles[1], DISPENSERSTYLE_BUILTIN1, stStyles[2], DISPENSERSTYLE_BUILTIN2, stStyles[3], DISPENSERSTYLE_COMMERCIAL, stStyles[4]
! ----------------------------------------------------------------------------- ! Default Sizes ! -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "iDispenserstyle" then a = defaultSizes[iDispenserstyle][1] b = defaultSizes[iDispenserstyle][2] zzyzx = defaultSizes[iDispenserstyle][3] parameters a = a, b = b, zzyzx = zzyzx endif if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "A" or GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "iDispenserstyle" then halfA = a/2 parameters halfA = halfA else if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "halfA" or GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "" then A = 2*halfA parameters A = A endif endif
! ----------------------------------------------------------------------------- ! Symbol Types ! ----------------------------------------------------------------------------- values{2} "iSymbolType" SYMBTYPE_DETAILED, stSymbTypes[1], SYMBTYPE_SIMPLE, stSymbTypes[2]
! ----------------------------------------------------------------------------- ! Limitations ! -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
if iDispenserstyle = 1 then values "a" range [0.1,) values "b" range [0.1,) values "zzyzx" range [0.1,) hideparameter "RollRadius", "iSymbolType", "CabinetLineType", "CabinetMat", \ "DoorMat", "FlangeMat", "HoodMat", "AccMat", "matDoorFrame", "matDoorPanel", "FlangeBracketMat" endif if iDispenserstyle = 2 then values "A" range [(BoxThk)*2+0.01*2+0.01,) values "B" range [0.02,) values "ZZYZX" range [(BoxThk)*2+0.05,) values "RollRadius" range [0.02,MIN((ZZYZX-(BoxThk)*2-0.002*2)/2,B-BoxThk+RollRadius*0.25+0.01)] hideparameter "doorMat", "accMat", "matSteel", "matDoorFrame", "matDoorPanel", "FlangeMat" if iDetlevel3D = DETLEVEL3D_SIMPLE then lock "HoodMat" endif if iDispenserstyle = 3 then values "A" range [(BoxThk)*2+0.01*2+0.01,) values "B" range [0.02,) values "ZZYZX" range [(BoxThk)*2+0.05,) values "RollRadius" range [0.02,MIN((ZZYZX-(BoxThk)*2-0.002*2)/2,B-BoxThk-0.01)] hideparameter "HoodMat", "matSteel", "matDoorFrame", "matDoorPanel", "FlangeBracketMat" if iDetlevel3D = DETLEVEL3D_SIMPLE then lock "AccMat" endif if iDispenserstyle = 4 then values "a" range [0.1,) values "b" range [0.1,) values "zzyzx" range [0.1,) hideparameter "RollRadius", "iSymbolType", "CabinetLineType", "FlangeMat", "HoodMat", "doorMat", "matSteel", "FlangeBracketMat" lock "a", "b", "zzyzx" endif
if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "FlangeBracketMat" then FlangeMat = FlangeBracketMat parameters FlangeMat = FlangeMat endif if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "FlangeMat" then FlangeBracketMat = FlangeMat parameters FlangeBracketMat = FlangeBracketMat endif
if gs_cont_pen = 0 then parameters gs_cont_pen = 7 if gs_fill_pen = 0 then parameters gs_fill_pen = 91
